# GitHub language stats (Linguist).
# flight-meta is a Go service with a React/TypeScript frontend under web/.
# Keep Go as the primary language while still showing the real TypeScript
# frontend: vendor only the design-token stylesheet and the bulkiest UI
# components so the language bar reads Go first, TypeScript second. The whole
# frontend stays in the repo and is showcased in the README; this only affects
# the language bar. See:
# https://github.com/github-linguist/linguist/blob/master/docs/overrides.md
web/src/index.css linguist-vendored
web/src/components/Legal.tsx linguist-vendored
web/src/components/OfferCard.tsx linguist-vendored
web/src/components/SearchForm.tsx linguist-vendored
web/src/components/Settings.tsx linguist-vendored
